%load_ext autoreload
%autoreload 2

from deeptracktorch.model import deeptracknet

deeptracknet

Sequential(
  (0): Conv2d(1, 16, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1))
  (1): ReLU()
  (2): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  (3): Conv2d(16, 32, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1))
  (4): ReLU()
  (5): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  (6): Conv2d(32, 64, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1))
  (7): ReLU()
  (8): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  (9): Flatten()
  (10): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=32, bias=True)
  (11): ReLU()
  (12): Linear(in_features=32, out_features=32, bias=True)
  (13): ReLU()
  (14): Linear(in_features=32, out_features=2, bias=True)
)
import fastai
from fastai.vision import *
from fastai.vision.data import PointsProcessor
from pathlib import Path
imagepath=Path('../data')

fn2ctr = pickle.load(open(imagepath/'imagepoints.pkl', 'rb'))
fn2ctr = {itm:torch.tensor(fn2ctr[itm]) for itm in fn2ctr}

data = (PointsItemList.from_folder(path=imagepath)
        .split_by_folder(train='train',valid='valid')
        .label_from_func(lambda o:fn2ctr[o.name])
        .databunch(bs=32)
       )


for itemList in ["train_dl", "valid_dl", "fix_dl", "test_dl"]:
   itemList = getattr(data, itemList)
   if itemList: itemList.x.convert_mode = "L"
  

learn = Learner(data, deeptracknet)

learn.fit(1)
learn.save('v1')
epoch train_loss valid_loss time
0 0.050438 0.074585 00:40 
hs=51/2
f,ax=plt.subplots(2,5,figsize=(16,10))
for i in range(10):
    img = data.valid_ds[i][0]
    x,y = data.valid_ds[i][1].data.numpy()[0]
    x=hs+(x*hs)
    y=hs+(y*hs)
    
    p=learn.predict(img)
    xp = hs+(p[2][0]*hs)
    yp = hs+(p[2][1]*hs)
    
    img.show(ax=ax[i%2,i//2])
    #ax[i%2,i//2].arrow(y,x,yp-y,xp-x,length_includes_head=True,fc="k", ec="k",head_width=2, head_length=2 )
    ax[i%2,i//2].plot(y,x,'k.')
    ax[i%2,i//2].plot(yp,xp,'rx')

learn.fit_one_cycle(10)
